{
  "stem": "10829.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "This is what we had.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So we decided that we're going to go to America, join our friends.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So we went up with our friends in the camp, becoming traitors, if you may.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Because we left them to go this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And we didn't believe in going to fight our cause.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Because we still had a cause.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We still had to go over and take Palestine.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And we decided to leave it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So we got it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We went in, and we told the commandant that we want to go.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "It took us two or three days till we finally got arranged for a telephone call to America to see through the camp.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And we told them we want to go.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And they had to start making papers to bring us out.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "So when we announced that, we had to get on the quota to come to America.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Although my mom and them we're going to take us out.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "But a quota-- And we couldn't stay in this camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And it's-- you got to, you got to realize what the times and situation is.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "There's two kids who are without a country, without a camp, and without a purpose, and traitors.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "So when you went from one camp, a DP camp, where you going?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "You're going to America.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "It was sort of a dirty word to us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "So we had to wait for a quota.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Quota system in those days were-- so you had to have the right time.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were a sister and brother, so you had to wait.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The time, sister and brother, the age, everything had to be in order to be your turn.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we waited from '48 till-- we waited over a year till we got the quota to come to America.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
